BuildRequires:    R-MASS >= 7.3.50
BuildRequires:    R-stats >= 3.5.1
Requires:         R-MASS >= 7.3.50
Requires:         R-stats >= 3.5.1

%description
We present a method based on filtering algorithms to estimate the
parameters of linear regressions, i.e. the coefficients and the variance
of the error term. The proposed algorithms make use of Particle Filters
following Ristic, B., Arulampalam, S., Gordon, N. (2004, ISBN: 158053631X)
resampling methods.

